<HL>
   Who's News:
   Magnetek Inc.
</HL>
<DATE>
09/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS MAG
</CO>
<IN>
ELECTRICAL COMPONENTS AND EQUIPMENT (ELQ)
</IN>
<LP>
   MAGNETEK Inc. (Los Angeles) -- Frank Perna Jr.,
52-year-old president, was elected to the additional position
of chief executive officer, a newly created post of this
electrical equipment maker. Andrew G. Galef, 57, continues as
chairman.
</LP>
